              "free_text": [
                " A 15 mum self-supporting",
                "beryllium foil (Be: 99.72%, main impurities:",
                "C,Mg,Al,Si,Fe) was used as target and combined with a",
                "12.5 mum aluminum catcher foil. The target thickness",
                " (2.78+0.3 mg/cm2) was determined by weighing and",
                "inhomogeneity was tested with the energy loss of",
