          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For E(3He)=10-28 MeV beryllium foils of 15 and 25mum",
                " (for E(3He) high 23 MeV) were used. The loss of 11-C",
                "residual nuclei through the rear side of the target",
                "was compensated by a beryllium /catcher/ foil in",
                "front of the target. The thicknesses (2.78+-0.3 and",
                "4.62 and 0.4 mg/cm2) were chosen to be equal to that",
                "of the target and higher than the range of the 11-C",
                "recoils. The average projectile energy in the target is",
                "thus shifted to slightly higher values (dE <= 300 keV).",
                "Only the target foil had to be analyzed."
              ]
            }
          ],
